<img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1805/441006.jpg" alt="Tim du Toit Attorneys appoints Bittersuite as their integrated agency" width="184" height="106">Tim du Toit Attorneys is one of South Africa’s oldest and most respected law firms with more than 50 professionals located across four major branches in South Africa. Boasting over 80 years of successful legal service to large corporates and individuals alike, the new partnership with Bittersuite aims to enhance the firm’s prominent standing in the market and promote the professional expertise that Tim Du Toit Attorneys is known for.